Physical units in options file and conversions:
LENGTH, DIAMETER [cm]
MASS [g]
PRESSURE [mmHg]
1 Pa = 7.5e-3 mmHg
DENSITY [g / cm3] * coef1 = [mmHg / (cm^2/s^2)]
coef1 = 7.5e-4
VISCOSITY [mPa s] * coef2 = [mmHg s]
coef2 = 7.5e-6
WINDKESSEL PARAMETERS:
RESISTANCE [mmHg s cm-1]
Pa s m-3 = 7.5e-9 mmHg s cm-1
COMPLIANCE [cm3 mmHg-1]
m3 Pa-1 = 1.3333e8 cm3 mmHg-1
